The paper discusses the challenges of preserving and reproducing data analysis software environments, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The development of a snapshotting file system also involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper mentions the software landscape used to discover the Higgs boson, which suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB).
